screens.screen_desc: The screenshot displays a shopping app interface with a colorful background featuring toys and games. At the top, there's a search bar labeled "Search or ask a question." Below, the main section highlights three deals: "Recommended deal for you," "4+ star deal for you," and "Glow up under $25," each accompanied by images of products. The bottom section encourages users to continue shopping with deals showing discounts of 15% and 20% on various items, including a laptop stand. The overall layout is user-friendly and visually appealing, aimed at promoting various products.

flow_desc: A user requests to search for items within a shopping app. The flow begins on a vibrant shopping app interface, prominently featuring a "Search or ask a question" bar at the top. Below the search bar, users can see highlighted deals categorized into "Recommended deal for you," "4+ star deal for you," and "Glow up under $25," each showcasing relevant product images. The layout is designed to be user-friendly and aesthetically pleasing, encouraging users to explore deals offering discounts of 15% and 20% on various products, including a laptop stand. The key action involves inputting search items into the designated text field.
